name: STOMACH TUBES
description:
## COMPOSITION
- 100% PVC, 100% DEHP-FREE PVC and 100% Silicone

## STERILIZATION
- Ethylene Oxide (EO) Sterile

## PRESENTATIONS
- PVC, DEHP-FREE PVC and Silicone
- Color-Coded Size Identification
- Standard and Ent-Fit Cponnector
- Encapsulated radiopaque stripe all along the tube length
- Highly Visible Size Indication every 5cm along the Tubing

## PERFORMANCE
- Smooth surface allowing successful introduction

## ANESTHASIA
- ENTERAL FEEDING THERAPY
